    ["D"] = "You\'ve made your pledge, $c.  Now it is up to you to see it through.$B$BServe the Scale of the Sands well and you will be rewarded.$B$BFail and the timeline as we know it will be unravelled!",
    ["O"] = "Bring your Band of Eternity to Soridormi at the Caverns of Time after obtaining Honored reputation with the Scale of the Sands.",
    ["T"] = "Sage\'s Vow",
  },
